Kappy is a budget planner app, that allows you to manage expenses and Income at one place.
It comes with a Subscription plan called Kappy plus. 
Kappy plus subscription provides you with following features:

1. Ads are removed permanently with jut one time payment.
2. Payment will be charged from your itunes connect acconut
3. Payment once done, will enroll you for kappy plus subscription for lifetime. 
4. It is non consumable subscription that dont needs renewal after specific time
